{"tid":1447981,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"「警察還眼」明天1PM全民入機場 百萬人塞爆機場","createTime":"2019-08-11T16:19:38.000Z","updateTime":"2019-08-11T16:41:58.000Z","uid":214272,"like":16,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":7,"replies":[{"pid":"9e6b056a102c22bcdd08dc9b70cd1ffc0bc26197","tid":1447981,"uid":214272,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-11T16:19:38.000Z","msg":"812起 1PM，有人性既你立刻罷工，百萬人進入機場，咩都唔做，勢要討回雙眼<br />\n機場因為100萬人係機場而暫停運作，不是們的責任，是因為機場不夠大<br />\n圍到出青馬，都全條橋唔夠闊<br />\n<br />\n統一口號，兩句，要入健力士，等歷史知道<br />\n「黑警還眼」<br />\n「五大訴求，缺一不可」<br />\n<br />\n黑警聽住：<br />\n一係你就入機場殺哂所有人<br />\n一係你就還返隻眼出黎<br />\n否則百萬人不離開機場<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n大群：<a href=\"https://t.me/airport730\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ft.me%2Fairport730&d=6RyWY35l7oH3ui7gcEo%2FTPDXWQKahOldmH8%2Bpia8yKE%3D&h=d4709493\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://t.me/airport730</a><br />\n實時Channel: <a href=\"https://t.me/hk730air\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ft.me%2Fhk730air&d=6RyWY35l7oH3ui7gcEo%2FTPDXWQKahOldmH8%2Bpia8yKE%3D&h=0f4b79de\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://t.me/hk730air</a>"},{"pid":"130e395b53ca1795e9671768486b1a1da6a69cb4","tid":1447981,"uid":214272,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-11T16:21:55.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"73a2be92c30acc7517e28e9b42e07715b305086b","tid":1447981,"uid":214272,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-11T16:22:06.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"04896748ab9d29a57806acea54eda3a6cb79c92f","tid":1447981,"uid":214272,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-11T16:22:22.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"0e5431c0ca4c269136886e0e83f56f4650d3c9fe","tid":1447981,"uid":202119,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-11T16:22:46.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"665eb4003d7e9754b9ce04413c0ac6953f7eaa06","tid":1447981,"uid":30982,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-11T16:22:56.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"285aa98